item.title: CVE-2021-24130|2024-08-03T19:21:18.661Z -- unknown -- wp%20google%20map%20plugin
item.description: Unvalidated input in the WP Google Map Plugin WordPress plugin, versions before 4.1.5, in the Manage Locations page within the plugin settings was vulnerable to SQL Injection through a high privileged user (admin+).
